dct_title_s: Vinnyt︠s︡i︠a︡, plan mista 1:18 000 : + t︠s︡entralʹna chastyna mista, okolyt︠s︡i mista / Kartohrafii︠a︡ ; redaktory--H.M. Koshova, R.M. Haldet︠s︡ka. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: City street map showing generalized land use and house-numbering system. Title from panel. "© DNVP 'Kartohrafii︠a︡', 2002, 2004, 2007-2014, 2017. © Ukrheodezkartohrafii︠a︡, 2002." Inset map on recto: Central Part. Ancillary map on verso: Surroundings of Vinnytsia. Includes city-center inset map, text, indexes, directories, city region map, city chronology, key to abbreviations, and color illustrations on verso.
